sets.title: Back & bicep charger
sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Intermediate week 10

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
Get set to maximize the power in your back and biceps.

A mini drop set will challenge your muscles to failure, so lock in good form with the exercise tutorials.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Get your body ready for a strong workout.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: This big compound move requires big effort – and a mini drop set.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Control your pace to max time under tension.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: Take your back and biceps to the limit.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Superset finish for an epic bicep pump.
